properties.name: 12 South Taproom
properties.description: Posted by Iphone.Oj508mUb1NWfBNOxXN6dMSozrg4= Small little beer joint with a great front porch and live music. Casual, no-pressure atmosphere.

properties.name: Café Coco
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl 222 22nd Ave N Ste 300, Nashville, TNOff-beat coffee house, restaurant, bar and music venue, Coco is perfect for a date, night out, or drinks after work. Great coffee while avoiding the Starbucks crowd. Music in the back is always interesting. Wonderful patio under a pergola. Awesome people-watching and free wifi makes this a must-visit!

properties.name: Grins Café
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Vegetarian/Vegan/Kosher cuisine on the Vandy campus. Time your visit so you miss the vandy kids\' lunch rush. Best wraps in town - try the Hummus wrap or the apple/peanut butter wrap.

properties.name: Harlow: A Salon on Music Row
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Best hair & makeup in Nashville! Small salon with serious talent. Enjoy drinks & snacks while you\'re being pampered.

properties.name: Jersey Mike's Elliston
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Standard subs/chips/sodas fare. What makes this location stand out is the awesome staff and the frighteningly delicious cookies. Avoid the lunch rush by calling ahead with your order.

properties.name: Mafiaoza's
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl 1205 Linden Ave # B, Nashville, TNBest pizza in Nashville!

properties.name: Mafiaoza's
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Best pizza in Nashville, 2-for-1 drinks on Thursday nights

properties.name: Rotier's
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Hole-in-the-wall restaurant that\'s a Nashville classic. Meat-and-three menu. Rumored to be the inspiration for Jimmy Buffett\'s "Cheeseburger in Paradise." Make sure you order a burger on french bread.

properties.name: Rumours Wine & Art Bar
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Wine starting at /glass, 4/bottle. Lovely patio and intimate interior.

properties.name: The Princeton Review
properties.description: Posted by Thronedl Test prep for college/grad entrance exams. Best teaching staff in the city, small offices. Free practice tests offered every once in a while.
